Package: snt
Type: Package
Title: The Official R Package for Subnational Tailoring of Malaria 
  Interventions (SNT)
Version: 1.4.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Mohamed A.", "Yusuf",
         role = c("aut", "cre"),
         email = "moyusuf@who.who",
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9339-4613",
         second_email = "mohamedayusuf87@gmail.com")))
Description: This package provides a suite of analytical tools to support the 
        subnational tailoring (SNT) of malaria interventions, enabling 
        evidence-based decision-making at the district level. It provides 
        functions for data management, cleaning, and analysis, including 
        malaria risk stratification and intervention targeting.
